{"_type":"issue","id":"beadflow-208","title":"Spring layout spreads independent clusters too far apart","description":"When there are multiple disconnected clusters in the visible graph, the force simulation spreads them too far apart. Independent clusters should be arranged compactly within a circular area rather than in a line. Consider adding a cluster-aware bounding force or initializing cluster positions in a circular arrangement before simulation.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","assignee":"Philipp Meier","owner":"projects@philipp.meier.name","created_at":"2026-05-05T07:08:03Z","created_by":"Philipp Meier","updated_at":"2026-05-05T07:14:35Z","started_at":"2026-05-05T07:13:50Z","closed_at":"2026-05-05T07:14:35Z","close_reason":"Closed","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"beadflow-208","depends_on_id":"beadflow-pyt","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-05-05T09:09:40Z","created_by":"Philipp Meier","metadata":"{}"}],"dependency_count":1,"dependent_count":0,"comment_count":0}
